2052.subject: ASAP
2052.descrlong: Provides supplemental support for BUS 204 Business Statistics course. Students work in small groups with a tutor from the Academic Skills Achievement Program (ASAP) and receive assistance on course assignments and study skills. Groups meet one hour per week. Credit/no credit only. (Offered every semester.)
